nodes.title: Upscaling Note
widgets_values:
The ultimate upscale takes a while, but it can be bypassed! Lightning models means it is faster than normal.

If you want to stop the upscale and do another SDTune image, simply go back to Tune Image Select and click "Cancel Current Run" This will allow you to progress another image or set of images for the SD Tune HQ workflow section.

Do not use : other punctuation can cause errors.

Feel free to have fun with wildcards! Styles, composition, pose, modifiers, word lists are all tons of fun. Use an LLM to make some of your own! Copy the prompt from the frame you want below to reinforce the style.

Changes to settings in the bottom section only apply once "Queue Prompt" is pressed again.

Try different IP Adapter settings! Plus is best for transfering style. Try style adaption and lower strength as well, or different start and end points for the IP adapter. 

Copy and paste the prompt from the SD Tune Prompt section to these prompt boxes below for better adherence. Note the sdtune prompts start at '0'.

If you want to turn off lightning for the bottom section, simply load a new checkpoint and connect to the 3 nodes above.
